name: Simulation cloud 8
description:
This interactive scene is 3D snapshot taken from a real-time 3D particle simulation developed in Three.js, where various force fields shape a particle cloud. The simulation can be stopped at specific moment and downloaded as a GLB file, to be explored in this app (find more info at www.lumicles.xyz). 
Check the help icon to learn how to control the cameras to navigate through the cloud and change the visualization parameters.

The app is not designed for mobile, event though it may run in some devices, mid to high end GPU is recommended
